= Xlib - a C Language Library interface to the X Window System Protocol =
== Introduction ==

This is the libX11 library that is the C binding to the X protocol. It is the foundation of practically every X Window System program out there. It is now in the freedesktop [http://cvs.freedesktop.org/xlibs/X11/ CVS].

== Mailing list ==

All Xlib discussion is currently on [http://freedesktop.org/mailman/listinfo/xlibs xlibs@freedesktop.org] mailing list.

Also join us on #freedesktop on [http://freenode.net freenode].

== CVS ==

Specification and implementation are in module X11 in [http://cvs.freedesktop.org/xlibs CVS].

